core::char::methods::<impl char>::is_asc.doc:
Checks if the value is within the ASCII range.

# Examples

```
let ascii = 'a';
let non_ascii = '❤';

assert!(ascii.is_ascii());
assert!(!non_ascii.is_ascii());
```

